==评价==
这部电影在日本的首周票房达8200多万日元<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.tokyohive.com/article/2014/06/japan-box-office-report-6-216-22|title= Japan Box Office Report – 6/21~6/22|date= 25 June 2014|accessdate= 26 June 2014|work= tokyohive|publisher= 6Theory Media, LLC|archive-date= 2014-06-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140627131319/http://www.tokyohive.com/article/2014/06/japan-box-office-report-6-216-22|dead-url= no}}</ref>，名列第五<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-06-30/japanese-box-office-june-21-22/.76114|title=Japanese Box Office, June 21–22|date=June 30, 2014|accessdate=June 30, 2014|publisher=Anime News Network|archive-date=2019-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526151324/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-06-30/japanese-box-office-june-21-22/.76114|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但评论不佳，[[日本雅虎|日本雅虎]]电影频道给出2.91分（满分5分），不少爱好者表示有负期待<ref name="tokyohive">{{cite web|url= http://www.tokyohive.com/article/2014/06/japan-box-office-report-6-216-22|title= Japan Box Office Report – 6/21~6/22|date= 25 June 2014|accessdate= 26 June 2014|work= tokyohive|publisher= 6Theory Media, LLC|language= en|archive-date= 2014-06-27|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140627131319/http://www.tokyohive.com/article/2014/06/japan-box-office-report-6-216-22|dead-url= no}}</ref>。第二周影片以{{JPY|38000000}}位居第八<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-07-06/japanese-box-office-june-28-29/.76377|title=Japanese Box Office, June 28–29|date=July 6, 2014|accessdate=September 20, 2014|publisher=Anime News Network|archive-date=2019-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191024234138/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-07-06/japanese-box-office-june-28-29/.76377|dead-url=no}}</ref>，第三周则跌至第12名，并最终收获{{JPY|24000000}}票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-07-17/japanese-box-office-july-5-6/.76664|title=Japanese Box Office, July 5–6|date=July 17, 2014|accessdate=September 20, 2014|publisher=Anime News Network|archive-date=2019-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526151510/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-07-17/japanese-box-office-july-5-6/.76664|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而在中国市场则收获了{{CNY|37900000}}票房<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.cbooo.cn/m/620150|script-title= zh:圣斗士星矢：圣域传说（2016）|accessdate= October 26, 2016|work= cbooo.cn|language= zh-cn|archive-date= 2017-07-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170723101731/http://www.cbooo.cn/m/620150|dead-url= no}}</ref>。

